SELECT `Lease Number`, `Unit Number`, Fld_Field_22 AS `Actual Out`, Fld_Field_3 AS `Commencement`, Fld_Field_30 AS `Delete Status`, Fld_Field_9 AS `Delivery or Effective`, Fld_Field_12 AS `End`, Fld_Field_5 AS `Execution`, Fld_Field_29 AS `Is Processed?`, Fld_Field_23 AS `NNN From Delivery`, Fld_Field_13 AS `Original End`, Fld_Field_4 AS `Override Commencement`, Fld_Field_11 AS `Plan Out`, Fld_Field_18 AS `Prior Version #`,
cast(DATE_FORMAT(STR_TO_DATE(Fld_Field_6,'%m/%d/%Y'),'%Y-%m-%d') as date) AS `ProcessingDate` ,
Fld_FKey_Field_19 AS `PV Lease Status`, Fld_Field_20 AS `PV Plan Out Date`, Fld_Field_21 AS `PV Version End Date`, Fld_Field_14 AS `RCD Days`, Fld_Field_28 AS `RCD Language`, Fld_Field_31 AS `Record Sent to JDE?`, Fld_Field_10 AS `Rent Start`, Fld_Field_15 AS `Round Up`, Fld_Field_27 AS `Tenant Name`, Fld_Field_26 AS `Tenant Number`, Fld_Field_8 AS `Term (Months)`, FLD_FIELD_25 AS `TI / FASB Ind Description`, Fld_FKey_Field_24 AS `TI / FASB Indicator`, Fld_FKey_Field_7 AS `Transaction Type`, Fld_FKey_Field_1 AS `Type`, Fld_Field_2 AS `Version #`, Fld_Field_16 AS `Version Effective`, Fld_Field_17 AS `Version End` FROM v_xl_tbl_section_14 WHERE CAST(DATE_FORMAT(STR_TO_DATE(Fld_Field_6,'%m/%d/%Y'),'%Y-%m-%d') AS DATE) BETWEEN DATE_ADD(NOW(),INTERVAL - 11 MONTH) AND NOW() limit 1000
